                        <interp inst="t18370612-name-1138" type="given" value="JAMES MORGAN"></interp>JAMES MORGAN STRACHAN</persName>
                  </hi>, Esq. I live at Teddington. I do not know the prisoner—he was never in my service—I have no son—I never sent the prisoner for these articles.</p>
